('real-estate-appraiser-moex-00112', 'real-estate-appraiser', 'real-estate-appraiser-moex-109-ba81c82b', 'sub-real-estate-appraiser-04', NULL, 'essay', '房地合一課徵所得稅制實施後，多年來不動產市場未達房市交易量基本
